text: The material in IRM 4.1.20 is obsolete because of changes in the LB&I organization and business practices. Relevant current material is contained in IRM 4.50.2, LB&I Compliance Integration, Other Workload Selection - Non-Campaign Workstreams and IRM 1.1.24, Organization and Staffing, Large Business and International Division.
EFFECT ON OTHER DOCUMENTS IRM 4.1.20 dated July 7, 2007 is superseded.
